      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been preserved with the highest level of care. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original luster and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in 'as-new' condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership.",
