    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. It currently does not run, likely due to a major engine issue, and the body shows heavy rust, several large dents, and peeling clear coat. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a missing headliner, making this an ideal candidate for a dedicated mechanic's project or a valuable source of spare parts. Please come prepared with a trailer, as it will need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 4200.0,
