    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$3,500 - Calling all project seekers and DIY mechanics! This vehicle is the perfect entry-level project for someone looking to hone their restoration skills. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a solid foundation and a great opportunity to build something special from the ground up. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge and a car with potential, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 3500.0,
